text: President Joe Biden is in Houston today to attend a campaign fundraiser. It's the second day of his latest Texas trip. The Democratic president flew into Dallas on Wednesday, where he attended two fundraisers. On Monday of this week, Harris County Judge Lina Hidalgo went to a Women's History Month reception in Washington, D.C. Biden, First Lady Jill Biden, and Vice President Kamala Harris were present at the event.
title: Biden Visits Texas For Campaign Fundraisers | Talk Radio 1190
author: @talkradio1190
